      • checkStudentAbsenses

        public int checkStudentAbsenses​(java.lang.String name)
        A method to check the number of absenses of a student. If she/he has made more or equal than 10 and less than 20, his/her mark average will be reduced %10. If she/he has made more or equal than 20, %20.
        Returns:
        A message that says if the mark average was reduced, and if it was, it says how much.

      • checkTeacherAbsenses
